reviewText: Stuff you will never see on main stream media

This man is brilliant.  A tough, emotional issue, but Trent really uses logic here and makes you think beyond what secular society deems as normal and acceptable.  A deeper look into the objective truth of the matter.  So worth watching no matter what your political bent.
Well thought out and well presented, his arguments are logical and persuasive.
A good and not too long video to help with sidewalk counseling in a loving and non-combative manner.  A good training tool.
